Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A SINGLE SHARD OF COURAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NCould it be Dai and Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not my concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my business anymore\Nwhether they live or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the Mage\Nfrom the fake Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Masopho.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a looter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a lot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!\NI'm a student of Aban, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a small-time crook like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?\NSo does the famous Aban
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,make students of people\Nwho abandon their companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?! Old man Burasu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody should help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, even if I go,\Nwhat can I do against Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Hero is one with courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And true courage is not planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,True courage does not depend\Non the strength of one's foes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not my words.\NThey were my master's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young, I trained to be\Na Mage to fight for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't hack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I would often abandon my companions\Nand run away from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And just look at me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While there's still a single shard\Nof courage left within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You disgust me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am disgusting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I do is think of myself and run away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While Master Aban and Dai\Nalways risked their lives to fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that kid's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is a student of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban?! You mean the real Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's made of different stuff than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A Heyedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She won't get in your way now.\NGo ahead and finish Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,save Dai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it will finally end...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with this blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Mage from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What can someone like you\Npossibly do by showing up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Aban, one fifth,\Nno, one tenth of what you had is enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lend me your courage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt my friends! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I'm going to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumb lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Don't attack that Lump Shaman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I recognize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You kidnapped him from the island\Nand turned him into your servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty fiends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Crocodine's Magic Cylinder...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to Dai,\Nyou're nothing but a gutless worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now and I'll spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that!\NI'm never abandoning my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban didn't train any cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine! Fight me one on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A puny ant like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you going to use a hostage\Nagainst a gutless worm like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're a worm, too!\NYou dumb lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! If it's death you seek, you can\Ngo with your friends to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Burasu! Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good. Now I can fight\Nwithout worrying about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see if my best spell will work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You distanced yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Heroes and Warriors, Mages like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are physically no different\Nfrom normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One blow from me will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it depends on whether the spell\Nyou want to cast will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself\Nwhether it'll work or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you are a worm,\Nyou're Aban's student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect\Nyou to be able to cast Merazoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I created a shield of wind\Nwith my Vortex Axe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and avoided a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're ready, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hurts! It hurts so bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... done for!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Run... Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not running anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You kept fighting\Nafter taking tons of blows like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be lying down\Nafter just one or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just have to sacrifice myself\Nand do what I can!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I can't bring it\Nto a stalemate like Master Aban, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait... Like Master Aban?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never done it before,\Nbut I'll have to try!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you endure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do with your rod shattered\Nand your Magic Power spent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all planned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shattering my rod\Nand saving my Magic Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the legendary spell\Nmy master, Aban, excelled at!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark influence, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mahokator!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I did... it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?\NWhat happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were under the Dark Army's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dirty plot\Nto use you against Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you can't leave that magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Use me against Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahokator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spell that creates\Na magic circle that repels evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cover an entire island\Nlike Master Aban, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! What point is there\Nin saving Burasu now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. You used a major spell\Nbeyond your abilities and you're spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's still... Dai's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If old man Burasu is okay,\Nthen Dai can fight freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll take care of you easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were willing\Nto sacrifice yourself for Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing noble like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still got my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To live on after having\Nabandoned my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought that would be\Nmore pathetic than dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Aban...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Popp,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the power we gain through\Ntraining should be used to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I get it now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry it took so long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This fledgling of a boy\Nis risking his life to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, look at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I abandoned my pride out of fear\Nand resorted to dirty schemes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this truly the right way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is victory worth\Nif it's at the cost of my pride?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit, Crocodine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing?!\NKill the boy already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Victory is at hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to lose your seat as\NLegion Commander over feelings of mercy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, run! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Stay inside the magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you step out of there,\Nall my hard work will be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tiny magic circle,\Nbut it contains all of my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He stands?! But Dai was all but finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, you'll pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You used my Grampa for evil\Nand hurt my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mark?! And this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be some hidden power of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that strange mark\Nresponds to Dai's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, Dai is truly angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His anger is exploding\Nat the Dark Army's dirty schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this Dai's true power that\Nforced Lord Hadorra to retreat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't lose here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I lose, what did I\Nthrow my pride away for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must win even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Dai's unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a Hoimi. You should be able to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Help Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body may be like steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but at close range, this will end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With my greatest, most powerful attack,\NI send you to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Dai! The attack of our master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An impressive attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You... win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If losing was my fate,\NI wish I'd fought you fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me a lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on how valuable pride really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If my defeat is by ones\Nsuch as you, I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was obsessed with victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero must always be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot Crocodine. He lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what was that astonishing power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that mark?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must inform Lord Hadorra\Nof the situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crocodine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having defeated the Beast King Crocodine,\NDai and friends head to Papnica Kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, they learn a terrible truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On their way to Leona, the party\Nis surrounded by undead monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then, a mysterious man\Ncarrying an ominous sword appears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Onto Papnica Kingdom"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
